General.Name: Corazon Mining Ltd
General.Description: Corazon Mining Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral resources. It primarily explores for nickel, cobalt, copper, and gold. The company's flagship project is its 100% owned Lynn Lake Nickel-Copper-Cobalt Sulphide Project located in Manitoba, Canada. The company was formerly known as Xanadu Resources Limited and changed its name to Corazon Mining Limited in June 2010. Corazon Mining Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
